{"id": "art-159", "label": "Art. 159", "title": "Art. 159", "slug": "art-159", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 159 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_454430909\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2016\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_454430909\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Societatea pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> va\navea 3 cenzori <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> un supleant, dac&#259; prin\nactul constitutiv nu se prevede un num&#259;r mai mare. În toate cazurile,\nnum&#259;rul cenzorilor trebuie s&#259; fie impar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_340054825\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2015\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_340054825\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Cenzorii sunt <span class=SpellE>ale&#351;i</span> de\nadunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>. Durata\nmandatului lor este de 3 ani <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pot fi <span\nclass=SpellE>reale&#351;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1753752664\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2014\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1753752664\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cenzorii trebuie s&#259; <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\nexercite personal mandatul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_585483604\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2013\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_585483604\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)La <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> cu capital majoritar de stat, unul dintre\ncenzori este, în mod obligatoriu, reprezentant al Ministerului Economiei <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}